PLEASE LEAVE BY JULY 31ST.

3
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:12,670
I don't believe this.

4
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:16,110
This isn't good.

5
00:00:16,110 --> 00:00:18,880
I'm late from the first day.

6
00:00:32,720 --> 00:00:34,190
I don't believe this.

7
00:00:34,890 --> 00:00:37,500
<i>The guy I liked a year
ago was there.</i>

8
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,700
Marimo.

9
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:46,000
Are you taking summer
lectures, too?

10
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:50,010
I want to go to the same
college as Rintarô.

11
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:52,610
See you later.

12
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:55,050
Bye.

13
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,190
Is that right?

14
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,500
I have to go to the
registration office.

15
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:11,460
We haven't received it yet.

16
00:01:11,930 --> 00:01:13,610
I don't believe this...

17
00:01:13,610 --> 00:01:15,304
There's been no payment?

18
00:01:15,304 --> 00:01:17,770
We received you application
for it, but we haven't

19
00:01:17,770 --> 00:01:18,970
received payment for it.

20
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:24,100
So you can't attend
the lecture today.

21
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:25,840
Please submit
payment immediately.

22
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,000
Yes.

23
00:01:32,850 --> 00:01:35,290
Julianne, it's time to eat.

24
00:01:41,890 --> 00:01:46,660
So the payment wasn't made...

25
00:01:48,130 --> 00:01:51,500
<i>I woke up late...</i>

26
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:53,640
<i>and rushed all the way here.</i>

27
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:56,310
<i>But I couldn't attend class.</i>

28
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:01,280
<i>Rintarô-senpai is
dating Satsuki.</i>

29
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:05,080
<i>And there was that
eviction notice on my door.</i>

30
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,190
<i>This is a bad day for me.</i>

31
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:16,360
Aren't you going
to attend your lecture?

32
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:19,200
I'm in trouble.

33
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,930
What's wrong?

34
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,900
I've fallen for you.

35
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,060
<i>I don't believe this!</i>

36
00:02:53,970 --> 00:02:57,140
<i>This is the start of a
confusing summer break.</i>

